09:50.367 --> 09:51.033
Oh, yeah.

09:51.033 --> 09:51.700
We did.

09:51.700 --> 09:52.967
Ask the historian.

09:52.967 --> 09:54.433
Yeah, I'm sorry, Donna.

09:54.433 --> 09:56.400
It's true.

09:56.400 --> 09:57.467
This is why you should never

09:57.467 --> 09:58.900
meet your heroes.

09:58.900 --> 09:59.800
When the founding fathers

09:59.800 --> 10:01.633
created our democracy, they gave

10:01.633 --> 10:03.933
the vote to just 6% of the

10:03.933 --> 10:05.100
population.

10:05.100 --> 10:06.633
And it took a long time to

10:06.633 --> 10:08.400
change that.

10:08.400 --> 10:10.533
(beeping, whirring)

10:10.567 --> 10:13.267
It took almost 70 years before

10:13.267 --> 10:14.633
the right to vote was extended

10:14.633 --> 10:16.100
even to just all white men.

10:16.100 --> 10:16.767
(dinging)

10:16.767 --> 10:18.233
White men rule.

10:18.267 --> 10:19.467
(all) White men rule!

10:19.467 --> 10:20.133
Here we go!

10:20.133 --> 10:21.133
White men rule!

10:21.133 --> 10:22.467
That's a bad chant.

10:22.467 --> 10:24.367
And then 14 years later, the

10:24.367 --> 10:25.967
Fifteenth Amendment finally gave

10:25.967 --> 10:27.567
black men the right to vote.

10:27.567 --> 10:28.600
(beeping)

10:28.633 --> 10:30.400
This will last forever!

10:30.400 --> 10:31.067
(laughing)

10:31.067 --> 10:31.733
Whoo!

10:31.733 --> 10:33.500
Yeah! (laughing)

10:33.533 --> 10:34.467
It didn't.

10:34.467 --> 10:36.100
Soon after that, states passed

10:36.100 --> 10:37.700
Jim Crow laws that made it

10:37.700 --> 10:39.300
virtually impossible for black

10:39.300 --> 10:40.700
Americans to vote.

10:40.733 --> 10:41.467
(beeping)

10:41.467 --> 10:43.367
I genuinely don't understand

10:43.367 --> 10:44.633
how we justify this to

10:44.633 --> 10:45.433
ourselves!

10:45.433 --> 10:46.567
(laughter)

10:46.600 --> 10:47.467
Awful.

10:47.467 --> 10:49.433
And, in 1920, women finally

10:49.433 --> 10:50.433
got the franchise.

10:50.467 --> 10:51.100
(beeping)

10:51.100 --> 10:52.400
Female president,

10:52.400 --> 10:53.667
here we come!

10:53.700 --> 10:55.300
(cheering)

10:55.300 --> 10:56.967
Get ready to wait, honey.

10:56.967 --> 10:59.800
And 45 years after that, the

10:59.800 --> 11:02.200
Voting Rights Act of 1965

11:02.200 --> 11:03.767
finally secured African

11:03.767 --> 11:05.633
Americans' right to vote.

11:05.633 --> 11:07.067
(beeping)

11:07.067 --> 11:09.433
Which brings us to the present.

11:09.433 --> 11:10.300
Who are all these people?

11:10.300 --> 11:12.267
I thought everyone could vote.

11:12.267 --> 11:13.367
Unfortunately not.

11:13.367 --> 11:14.967
There are still millions of

11:14.967 --> 11:17.133
American citizens who pay taxes

11:17.133 --> 11:19.233
and don't have representation.

11:19.233 --> 11:20.933
Those suffering without suffrage

11:20.933 --> 11:22.133
include the citizens of

11:22.133 --> 11:23.300
Washington, D.C...

11:23.300 --> 11:26.467
650,000 people live in D.C.

11:26.467 --> 11:27.467
and have no representation in

11:27.467 --> 11:28.133
Congress.

11:28.133 --> 11:28.967
(scoffing) Come on!

11:28.967 --> 11:30.300
And America's territories,

11:30.300 --> 11:31.400
like American Samoa,

11:31.400 --> 11:32.700
Puerto Rico, and Guam.

11:32.700 --> 11:33.867
We're American citizens.

11:33.867 --> 11:34.567
Jeez!

11:34.567 --> 11:35.300
And it gets worse--

11:35.300 --> 11:36.467
Worse, of course it does.

11:36.467 --> 11:37.700
What other nice people

11:37.700 --> 11:38.367
can't vote?

11:38.367 --> 11:40.300
Nuns, volunteers in nursing

11:40.300 --> 11:41.800
homes, Tom Hanks?

11:41.800 --> 11:43.133
Nope-- felons!

11:43.133 --> 11:44.733
In many states, felons are

11:44.733 --> 11:46.567
barred from voting for the rest

11:46.567 --> 11:47.867
of their lives, even after

11:47.867 --> 11:48.733
they're released.

11:48.733 --> 11:49.900
Well, isn't that a...

11:49.900 --> 11:51.367
good thing?

11:51.367 --> 11:52.767
I mean, maybe they

11:52.767 --> 11:53.767
