11:53.767 --> 11:54.800
Why?

11:54.800 --> 11:56.267
I served my time.

11:56.267 --> 11:56.967
What's the worst that could

11:56.967 --> 11:58.100
happen?

11:58.100 --> 11:59.967
(cackling)

