12:02.033 --> 12:04.467
It's "Purge" time, baby!

12:04.467 --> 12:05.133
Haa!

12:05.133 --> 12:06.967
Lady, that's preposterous.

12:06.967 --> 12:07.733
You have to vote for

12:07.733 --> 12:09.233
a candidate.

12:09.233 --> 12:10.533
I'm actually registered

12:10.533 --> 12:11.267
Green Party.

12:11.267 --> 12:12.800
Oh, gosh.

12:12.800 --> 12:14.200
You've got a good point there.

12:14.200 --> 12:16.033
Maybe I'm convinced.

12:16.033 --> 12:17.233
You know, guys, this topic

12:17.233 --> 12:18.533
has a really interesting

12:18.533 --> 12:19.200
history.

12:19.200 --> 12:20.433
Oh, yeah, good point, Ed.

12:20.433 --> 12:21.867
To learn more, let's go back in

12:21.867 --> 12:23.267
time to the Jim Crow South.

12:23.267 --> 12:24.800
I said I was convinced!

12:24.800 --> 12:26.800
(thunder crashing)

12:26.800 --> 12:28.067
(Adam) Here we are.

12:28.067 --> 12:29.800
Yeah, for 100 years in the

12:29.800 --> 12:31.567
Jim Crow South, white

12:31.567 --> 12:32.967
Southerners did everything they

12:32.967 --> 12:34.633
could to keep black Southerners

12:34.633 --> 12:35.300
from voting.

12:35.300 --> 12:36.067
Go on home.

12:36.067 --> 12:37.933
They would take minor crimes

12:37.933 --> 12:39.467
and turn them into felonies,

12:39.467 --> 12:41.567
and then pass laws saying that

12:41.567 --> 12:42.933
felons can't vote.

12:42.933 --> 12:44.067
I'd like to vote, please.

12:44.067 --> 12:45.200
Are you a felon?

12:45.200 --> 12:47.133
No, sir.

12:47.133 --> 12:49.033
Well, you are now, standing

12:49.033 --> 12:51.300
around this line like a vagrant.

12:51.300 --> 12:52.633
Let's go!

12:52.633 --> 12:54.067
How awful.

12:54.067 --> 12:55.367
Thank God all those laws have

12:55.367 --> 12:56.433
been repealed.

12:56.433 --> 12:57.600
I hate to tell you this,

12:57.600 --> 12:59.367
Donna, but a lot of laws like

12:59.367 --> 13:00.800
that are still on the books

13:00.800 --> 13:01.467
today.

13:01.467 --> 13:02.800
And they're still stopping

13:02.800 --> 13:04.600
African Americans from voting.

13:04.600 --> 13:07.600
Here, I'll show you.

13:07.600 --> 13:10.300
(energy crackling)

13:10.300 --> 13:12.300
Donna, this is Daryl Atkinson,

13:12.300 --> 13:13.733
a senior staff attorney at the

13:13.767 --> 13:14.800
Southern Coalition for Social

13:14.800 --> 13:15.467
Justice.

13:15.467 --> 13:16.200
Hey, how you doing, Donna?

13:16.200 --> 13:16.800
Hi.

13:16.800 --> 13:17.567
Adam, I've gotta go to court.

13:17.567 --> 13:18.233
Yeah, but, you could take

13:18.267 --> 13:19.367
