14:14.133 --> 14:15.600
Take me back to the polling

14:15.600 --> 14:16.267
place.

14:16.267 --> 14:17.533
That is a wonderful idea,

14:17.533 --> 14:18.200
Donna.

14:18.200 --> 14:18.867
(beeping)

14:18.867 --> 14:19.867
Too bad the political parties

14:19.867 --> 14:20.767
have rigged the system to

14:20.767 --> 14:21.600
determine the outcome of

14:21.600 --> 14:22.600
elections before they even

14:22.600 --> 14:23.467
happen.

14:23.467 --> 14:25.100
No!

14:25.100 --> 14:26.033
And I'll tell you about it

14:26.033 --> 14:26.800
tonight, on

14:26.800 --> 14:28.133
"Adam Ruins Everything,"

14:28.133 --> 14:30.067
Election Night Edition.

